				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: High Agro songs?<a name="52833"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 20 04 1:46 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Well....I'm assuming you are referring to PoV pulling, where you don't have mez/lull that is effective (at level 58).  If you pull two, you might consider using the level 51 snare/slow and/or some DoT songs (those are the only thing that generate better agro than assist).  So, in other words, you get two mobs, realize it before you get to camp, circle around a bit, till you can land snare on one, bring the other to camp, snare it, so tank can get agro, run back and grab agro on friend, and keep it away from camp, and assisting its friend. </span></td>
			</tr><tr>
